 1в†’/**
 2в†’ * sequant run - Execute workflow for GitHub issues
 3в†’ *
 4в†’ * Orchestrator module that composes focused workflow modules:
 5в†’ * - worktree-manager: Worktree lifecycle (ensure, list, cleanup, changed files)
 6в†’ * - phase-executor: Phase execution with retry and failure handling
 7в†’ * - phase-mapper: Label-to-phase detection and workflow parsing
 8в†’ * - batch-executor: Batch execution, dependency sorting, issue logging
 9в†’ */
10в†’
